        <chapter>
          <title>The GDP growth</title>
          <paragraph>The Swedish economy advanced a seasonally adjusted 0.5% on the quarter in the three months to March of 2016, following an upwardly revised 1.6% expansion in the previous period and missing market expectations of 0.7% growth.</paragraph>
